Day 12: Embrace Transparency!
🔍 "Transparency isn’t optional—it's essential!"  
👉 Tip: Ensure everything is visible to the team and stakeholders. A transparent process fosters trust and alignment.

💡 𝗗𝗮𝗶𝗹𝘆 𝘁𝗶𝗽𝘀 for Scrum Teams and especially Scrum Masters! Get practical advice, best practices, & strategies to boost collaboration and sprint success.
